<% title 'MIAM is out of date' %>
<% step_header %>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    <h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">Your MIAM is out of date</h1>

    <p class="govuk-body-l">
      You’re legally required to attend a <abbr title="Mediation Information and Assessment Meeting">MIAM</abbr> within
      4 months of your application, unless you have a valid reason.
    </p>

    <p class="govuk-body">
      <a href="/about/miam_exemptions" target="_blank" class="govuk-link">Check if you have a valid reason</a> before
      you continue with your application.
    </p>

    <h2 class="govuk-heading-l">If you don’t have a valid reason</h2>

    <section class="numbered-list">
      <ol class="govuk-list govuk-list--number">
        <li>
          <a href="https://www.familymediationcouncil.org.uk/find-local-mediator/" class="govuk-link" rel="external" target="_blank">Find
            a mediator</a> and book a <abbr title="Mediation Information and Assessment Meeting">MIAM</abbr>
        </li>
        <li>Attend the <abbr title="Mediation Information and Assessment Meeting">MIAM</abbr></li>
        <li>Ask the mediator for a document confirming your attendance</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <p class="govuk-body">You can then return to this form to continue with your application.</p>

    <h2 class="govuk-heading-l">If you are unsure, or think you have a valid reason</h2>

    <p class="govuk-body">You can continue using this service and we’ll try and work out if you have a valid reason based on your answers.</p>

    <div class="govuk-inset-text">
      If you do not have a valid reason you will not be able to make the application and will be directed to attend a
      <abbr title="Mediation Information and Assessment Meeting">MIAM</abbr>.
    </div>

    <%= link_button 'Confirm and continue', edit_steps_miam_exemption_claim_path %>
  </div>
</div>
